				<p>Pen, paper, paintbrush, stylus, pen tool &mdash; you name it, I'll end up drawing something with it.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<h3>Front-end Code &amp; Prototyping</h3>
				<p>I build and prototype my designs with HTML, CSS (LESS), jQuery, and a sprinkling of PHP and JavaScript.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="three-col minor">
			<div class="col">
				<h3>User Experience</h3>
